    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1879-12-05T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1879-12-05T00:00:00-05:00" n="549" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d549">
                <head>No. 549.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">St.
                                    Petersburg</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1879-12-05">
                            <hi rend="italic">December</hi> 5,
                            1879</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p rend="flushleft">
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Evarts</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Washington, District of Columbia:</hi>
                </p>
                <p>Train containing Emperor’s baggage and part of suite blown up—partially
                        wrecked—near Moscow. No one hurt. Generally considered attempt on Emperor’s
                        life.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>HOFFMAN.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
